          <li class="style3">
            <div align="left">A positive attitude is the key to success in any problem solving procedure or major lifestyle change. </div>
          </li>
          <li class="style3">
            <div align="left">With a consistently positive attitude, it is possible to win the game of life in all directions: personal satisfaction, strong relationships and success in a meaningful career. </div>
